        <h1 class="page-title">Tag</h1>
        <p class="page-desc">
          The Tag is a compact, interactive label component used to categorize, filter, or represent metadata that users can act upon. Tags support dismissal (close), leading elements (icons or status indicators), and multiple semantic color variants.
        </p>
